"https://api.github.com/repos/rwf2/Rocket/issues/1177","id":609020687,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDYwOTAyMDY4Nw==","user":{"login":"timando","id":10087761,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwMDg3NzYx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10087761?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando","html_url":"https://github.com/timando","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-04-04T12:21:52Z","updated_at":"2020-04-04T12:21:52Z","body":"I had a similar problem and I wrote the following code:\r\n```rust\r\npub struct TemplateRenderer<'a,'r>(&'a rocket::Request<'r>);\r\nimpl <'_a, '_r> TemplateRenderer<'_a, '_r>{\r\n    pub fn render<S,C>(&self,name: S, context: C) -> String\r\n    where S: Into<std::borrow::Cow<'static, str>>, C: serde::Serialize, S: std::fmt::Display\r\n    {\r\n        use rocket_contrib::templates::Template;\r\n        use rocket::response::Responder;\r\n        let template = Template::render(name.into(), context);\r\n        let mut response = template.respond_to(self.0).unwrap();\r\n        response.body_string().unwrap_or_else(String::new)\r\n    }\r\n}\r\nimpl<'a, 'r> rocket::request::FromRequest<'a, 'r> for TemplateRenderer<'a,'r>{\r\n    type Error = !;\r\n    fn from_request(request: &'a rocket::Request<'r>) -> rocket::request::Outcome<Self, Self::Error> {\r\n        rocket::request::Outcome::Success(TemplateRenderer(&request))\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rwf2/Rocket/issues/comments/609020687/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"timando","id":10087761,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwMDg3NzYx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10087761?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando","html_url":"https://github.com/timando","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timando/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rwf2/Rocket/issues/comments/1133189065","html_url":"https://github.com/rwf2/Rocket/issues/1177#issuecomment-1133189065","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rwf2/Rocket/issues/1177","id":1133189065,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAzqMt85DixfJ","user":{"login":"paul-hansen","id":7019130,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcwMTkxMzA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7019130?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen","html_url":"https://github.com/paul-hansen","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-05-20T18:21:23Z","updated_at":"2022-05-20T21:01:13Z","body":"Note that the workaround @timando proposed doesn't work with 0.5-rc because the lifetime of the references held by the Request is no longer exposed in the trait's signature. It's now `FromRequest<'r>` instead of `FromRequest<'a, 'r>` which as far as I can tell means we can't hold onto a reference to the request because there isn't a way to tie the lifetime of our struct's (TemplateRenderer in timando's code) Request to the lifetime of the trait's Request references.\r\n\r\nhttps://api.rocket.rs/v0.5-rc/rocket/request/trait.FromRequest.html\r\nhttps://api.rocket.rs/v0.4/rocket/request/trait.FromRequest.html\r\n\r\nProbably a good thing that it doesn't work anymore though since it works around this intentional limitation: https://rocket.rs/v0.5-rc/guide/faq/#raw-request\r\n\r\nStill would be nice to render a template for emails though.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rwf2/Rocket/issues/comments/1133189065/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"paul-hansen","id":7019130,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcwMTkxMzA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7019130?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/paul-hansen","html_url":"https://github.com/paul-hansen","